title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.info: Allows an application to request installing packages.
android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.description: Malicious applications can use this to try and trick users into installing additional malicious packages.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

manifest_analysis.title:
Service (core.QuickSettingsService) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: android.permission.BIND_QUICK_SETTINGS_TILE
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.
manifest_analysis.name: is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.[android:exported=true]

nx.description: The shared object has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object has a stack canary value added to the stack so that it will be overwritten by a stack buffer that overflows the return address. This allows detection of overflows by verifying the integrity of the canary before function return.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object has full RELRO enabled. RELRO ensures that the GOT cannot be overwritten in vulnerable ELF binaries. In Full RELRO, the entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) is marked as read-only.

rpath.description: The shared object does not have run-time search path or RPATH set.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

metadata.description: The App uses an insecure Random Number Generator.
metadata.cwe: CWE-330 Use of Insufficiently Random Values
CWE-312 Cleartext Storage of Sensitive Information
metadata.description: Files may contain hardcoded sensitive informations like usernames, passwords, keys etc.
App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.
metadata.cwe: CWE-89 Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')

metadata.description: The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.
metadata.cwe: CWE-532 Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File

metadata.description: App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.
App can read/write to External Storage. Any App can read data written to External Storage.
This App uses SSL certificate pinning to detect or  prevent MITM attacks in secure communication channel.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327 Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: MD5 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.
This App copies data to clipboard. Sensitive data should not be copied to clipboard as other applications can access it.

metadata.cwe: CWE-327 Use of a Broken or Risky Cryptographic Algorithm
metadata.description: SHA-1 is a weak hash known to have hash collisions.
This App uses RSA Crypto without OAEP padding. The purpose of the padding scheme is to prevent a number of attacks on RSA that only work when the encryption is performed without padding.
metadata.cwe: CWE-780 - Use of RSA Algorithm without OAEP

metadata.description: Insecure Implementation of SSL. Trusting all the certificates or accepting self signed certificates is a critical Security Hole. This application is vulnerable to MITM attacks

FCS_RBG_EXT.1.1.choice: The application invoke platform-provided DRBG functionality for its cryptographic operations.

FDP_NET_EXT.1.1.choice: The application has user/application initiated network communications.

FDP_DAR_EXT.1.1.choice: The application implement functionality to encrypt sensitive data in non-volatile memory.

FMT_MEC_EXT.1.1.choice: The application invoke the mechanisms recommended by the platform vendor for storing and setting configuration options.

FTP_DIT_EXT.1.1.choice: The application does encrypt some transmitted data with HTTPS/TLS/SSH between itself and another trusted IT product.

FCS_RBG_EXT.2.1,FCS_RBG_EXT.2.2.choice: The application perform all deterministic random bit generation (DRBG) services in accordance with NIST Special Publication 800-90A using Hash_DRBG. The deterministic RBG is seeded by an entropy source that accumulates entropy from a platform-based DRBG and a software-based noise source, with a minimum of 256 bits of entropy at least equal to the greatest security strength (according to NIST SP 800-57) of the keys and hashes that it will generate.

FCS_COP.1.1(1).choice: The application perform encryption/decryption in accordance with a specified cryptographic algorithm AES-CBC (as defined in NIST SP 800-38A) mode or AES-GCM (as defined in NIST SP 800-38D) and cryptographic key sizes 256-bit/128-bit.

FCS_COP.1.1(2).choice: The application perform cryptographic hashing services not in accordance with FCS_COP.1.1(2) and uses the cryptographic algorithm RC2/RC4/MD4/MD5.

FCS_COP.1.1(4).choice: The application perform keyed-hash message authentication with cryptographic algorithm ['HMAC-SHA1'] .

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.1.choice: The application implement the HTTPS protocol that complies with RFC 2818.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.2.choice: The application implement HTTPS using TLS.

FCS_HTTPS_EXT.1.3.choice: The application notify the user and not establish the connection or request application authorization to establish the connection if the peer certificate is deemed invalid.

FIA_X509_EXT.2.1.choice: The application use X.509v3 certificates as defined by RFC 5280 to support authentication for HTTPS , TLS.

FPT_TUD_EXT.2.1.choice: The application shall be distributed using the format of the platform-supported package manager.

"tunnel_config_smartlist_description" : "La fonctionnalité « liste intelligente » réduit considérablement le nombre de règles dans vos filtres. playstore_details.title: Adblock - No Ads. Better battery, faster browsing.
playstore_details.description:
Block annoying and intrusive ads while browsing or in your favorite apps.

AdBlock is an professional adblocker that runs on every Android phone & tablet. With advance interception technology (DNS), AdBlock enables you to have an ad free browsing experience to see only the content you want.

AdBlock blocks ads, banners, in app advertisment, adult & gambling websites and malicous websites. It can also prevent advertisers from tracking your behavior, improves privacy and data protection and saves battery as well as data plan. 
Blocking intrusive ads minimizes the risk of “malvertising” infections. Adblock disable known malware domains and makes protecting yourself from malware easy. 

Enhanced privacy inbuilt to disable tracking. Adblock lets you browse the web anonymously and stop companies from tracking your online activity.

You don't need to change your favorite browser for ad blocking. This application runs on all your favorite browser (include Google Chrome).

The best features at a glance:
- NO root permissions required!
- The application supports every web browser and adblock everything in .
- DNS based interception (VPN mode) for all modern browsers.
- Blocks sites that distribute malicious content, viruses and fraudulent websites.

The most compatible ad blocker on the market!

• ❎ Blocks ads
• 💰 Saves your data plan
• 🛵 Browse FASTER by loading 30% less data
• 🔋 Increase battery life
• 👩‍🏫 Inbuilt tester
• 🏖️ Super easy to use

💪Keep ads away
• Blocks annoying ads (eg. Google AdWords, Google Invite Media, DoubleClick Bid Manager, Liftoff, Bing Ads and Amazon)
• Blocks adult websites 
• Blocks gambling websites
• Blocks (social media) tracker (eg. Google Analytics, Facebook Connect, DoubleClick, Google Publisher Tags, Google AdSense, Twitter Button, Yandex.Metrix and Comscore)
• Blocks malicious websites (eg. Virus downloads, malicious content, fraudulent websites and manipulated Android apps)
• By saving at least 20% less data, they save their mobile data.
• Battery life will be longer if no animated banners or commercials are loaded.
• Plus Adblock Android App.

Source code: https://gitlab.com/rucksack.dev/adblock_and_anti-tracking
Upstream source code: https://github.com/blokadaorg/blokada

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Докоснете аватара си по-горе за да видите ID (идентификационния номер) на профила си. Не забравяйте, че идентификационния номер е поверителен и трябва да го пазите. Запишете го в случай, че деинсталирате приложението."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Napauta yllä olevaa avatariasi nähdäksesi tilitunnuksesi. Muista, että tilitunnuksesi on salainen, ja sinun tulee säilyttää se itselläsi. Kirjoita se muistiin, jos poistat sovelluksen."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Tapnite sliko zgoraj za vaš ID. Vaš ID je tajen in ga ne povejte drugim. Zapišite si ga za primer, če morate aplikacijo izbrisati."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Dotykom na váš avatar vyššie zistíte ID vášho účtu. Nezabudnite, že vaše ID je tajné a mali by ste si ho nechať pre seba. Zapíšte si ho v prípade, že odinštalujete aplikáciu."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "לחצו על האווטאר שלכם כדי לראות את מזהה החשבון שלכם. זכרו, המזהה שלכם הינו סודי ועליכם לשמור אותו לעצמכם. רשמו אותו למקרה שתסירו את האפליקציה."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Tik hierboven op uw avatar om je account-ID te zien. Vergeet niet dat je ID geheim is en je deze voor jezelf moet houden. Schrijf het op voor het geval je de app verwijdert."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Stuknij awatar powyżej, aby zobaczyć identyfikator konta. Pamiętaj, że twój identyfikator jest tajny i powinieneś zachować go dla siebie. Zapisz go na wypadek odinstalowania aplikacji."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "点击上面的头像来查看您的帐号ID。请记住，您的ID是保密的，您应该自己保留着它。如果您卸载应用程序，请将其记下。"

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "உங்கள் கணக்கின் அடையாளத்தை பார்க்க மேலே உள்ள உங்கள் அவதாரை தட்டவும், உங்கள் அடையாளத்தை நீங்கள் ரகசியமாக உங்களிடம் மட்டுமே வைத்து கொள்ளவும். இந்த செயலியை நீக்கும் பட்சத்தில் அதை ஓரிடத்தில் எழுதி வைத்து கொள்ளவும்."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "अपना खाता आईडी देखने के लिए ऊपर अपना अवतार को छुएं। याद रखें, आपकी आईडी गुप्त है और आपको इसे अपने पास ही रखना चाहिए। यदि आप ऐप को अनइंस्टॉल करते हैं तो इसे कहीं लिख लें।"
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Apasați pe poza dvs. pentru a vedea ID-ul contului. Tineți minte, ID-ul dvs. este secret si nu ar trebui să-l dați nimănui. Notați-l in caz ca veti dezinstala aplicația."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "アカウントIDを確認するには、上のアバターをタップしてください。IDは誰とも共有せずに保管してください。アプリをアンインストールする場合に備えて書き留めてください。"
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Toque seu avatar acima para ver o ID da sua conta. Lembre-se, seu ID é secreto e você deve mantê-lo para si. Anote-o caso desinstale o aplicativo."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Cliquez sur votre avatar ci-dessus pour voir l'identifiant de votre compte. N'oubliez pas que votre identifiant est secret et que vous ne devez pas le partager. Écrivez-le au cas où vous désinstalleriez l'application."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "아바타를 눌러 계정 ID를 보세요. 사용자의 ID는 사용자 혼자서 비밀로 기억해야 합니다. 앱 제거 시 다른 곳에 적어두세요."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Hesap kimliğinizi görmek için yukarıdaki avatarınıza dokunun. Unutmayın, kimliğiniz gizlidir ve bunu kendinize saklamalısınız. Uygulamayı kaldırmanız durumunda not alın."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Toca tu avatar arriba para ver tu ID de cuenta. Recuerda, tu ID es secreto y deberías guardarlo para ti mismo. Anótalo en caso de que desinstales la aplicación."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Tocca il tuo avatar qui sopra per vedere l'ID del tuo account. Ricorda, il tuo ID è segreto e dovresti tenerlo solo per te. Annotatelo nel caso in cui disinstallassi l'app."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Pressione no seu avatar acima para ver o ID da sua conta. Lembre-se, o ID é seu e deve mantê-lo em segredo. Anote-o para o caso de desinstalar a aplicação."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "A fiókazonosítód megtekintéséhez érintsd meg a fenti avatart. Ne felejtsd, hogy az azonosítód titkos, és titokban is kell tartanod. Írd fel valahova arra az esetre, ha eltávolítanád az alkalmazást."

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Нажмите на свой аватар выше, чтобы увидеть ID вашего аккаунта. Помните, что ваш ID необходимо хранить в тайне и хранить в надежном месте. Запишите его на случай удаления приложения."
"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "輕點您的大頭貼以檢視您的帳號 ID。請記住，您的 ID 是祕密，您應該將其保存在隱密的地方。如果您可能會解除安裝應用程式的話，請將其寫下來。"

"menu_vpn_account_secret" : "Klepnutím na váš avatar výše, zjistíte ID vašeho účtu. Nezapomeňte, že vaše ID je tajné a měli byste si ho nechat pro sebe. Zapište si ho v případě, že se chystáte aplikaci odinstalovat."
